y, if due to the bubbles, cannot be fully understood only by the\ninclination of bubbles' axis against the Galactic disk normal, thus suggesting\nasymmetric outflow due to different environmental/initial condition.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 22 May 2015 02:33:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-25"}
