ing Poynting fluxes and opens the door to more quantitative studies\nof the solar photosphere and more realistic data-driven simulations of coronal\nmagnetic field evolution.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 22 May 2015 07:44:17 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 11 Aug 2015 22:47:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-09-23"}
